snippet.title: Puzzle Bots trailer
snippet.description:
A teaser/trailer for "Puzzle Bots", the upcoming puzzle adventure game from Wadjet Eye Games!

Find out more at http://www.wadjeteyegames.com/puzzlebots.htm

Lead designer: Erin Robinson
Background art: John Green
Pixel sprites: Erin Robinson, Roberto Gracia, Craig Forrester
Music: Chris Moorson
Published by: Wadjet Eye Games
